Saying tanks don't build a single damage item is a lie though.  Almost every tank builds at least one of these items and most tanks build 2 or 3 of these items.  CDR is also an offensive stat for champions that rely on abilities to do damage so items like frozen heart and spirit visage could be considered offensive items for a tank.
